author: kahatlen
msg: Problem was that getCanonicalPath() needed a security permission on
Windows (but not on Solaris/Linux). In addition the Derby engine had
to be shut down before derby.log could be deleted on Windows.

The error was introduced when the new ResourceFileLoader for Texen was added.
